Version 0.1.0
=============
*Added PasswordField widget. A text field that receives text input but it's 
visual counterpart is replaced with asterisks instead of the actual text.
*Added IconProgressBar widget. A progress bar that fills itself with icons.
*Added UTF-8 support for text input widgets.
*Fixed an input problem, where widgets underneath the cursor that had lower 
z-order wouldn't receive a mouse entered event if widgets with higher z-order 
got hidden.
*Fixed a bug where empty TextField's were trying to access text rows that didn't
exist.
*New distributable events for Widgets indicating that an ancestor of them got 
shown/hidden.

